    {
      "text": "Gachapin (ガチャピン) is a TV character who appeared in the Japanese children's program Hirake! Ponkikki and its succeeding series Ponkickies on Fuji TV. He is a green buck-toothed anthropomorphic dinosaur and is usually accompanied by his friend Mukku, a red yeti with a yellow propeller on his head.",
